---
title: Creamy Bacon, Chicken & Parmesan Spaghetti with Baby Leaf Salad
description: This creamy spaghetti concoction comes together in a snap! With crispy bacon, chicken and baby leaves stirred through for a touch of vibrant greens, the beauty is in the simplicity of this meal. Sprinkle over a generous amount of Parmesan cheese and a pinch of chilli flakes if you’re feeling feisty!
